{"tid":1795791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國《金融時報》選出「be water」為三個年度字詞之一","createTime":"2019-12-24T07:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T16:05:39.000Z","uid":212626,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fb84171526d300190b1f6415c2cb0603137fce07","tid":1795791,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》發表評論文章，選出「be water」為其中一個年度字詞。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，已故武打巨星李小龍這句名言，成為今年香港抗爭者的策略。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，受到「be water」理念影響，抗爭者「如露」般堵塞主要道路或者包圍重要建築物；而當防暴警察集結驅散時，他們已經「如霧」地四散，「如水」一樣往橫街窄巷逃走；但一旦被捕，抗爭者就「如冰」地頑抗。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，這個理念影響到世界各地的抗爭者，由西班牙、智利到黎巴嫩，都借鏡港人的「be water」策略。<br />\n<br />\n李小龍在1970年代接受訪問時，解釋自己武術哲學，大意清空自己，像水一樣不受型態限制，在不同時候變化，作出流動或者攻擊，像水一樣既柔且剛。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499368-20191224.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499368-20191224.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=9756be39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499368-20191224.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=22aae502\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499368-20191224.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2439c7494feb4e4c7aee0b94ea5527a2f44e2e23","tid":1795791,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:23:52.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》同時選出 「Decoupling」及「We」為另外兩個年度字詞，兩個字分別指中美經濟脫鉤，及美國共享辦公室新創業者 WeWork 陷入財困兩宗新聞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1-%E9%81%B8%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%97%E8%A9%9E-be-water/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25AD%2597%25E8%25A9%259E-be-water%2F&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=671c2cb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25AD%2597%25E8%25A9%259E-be-water%2F&h=3acc13c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1-%E9%81%B8%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%97%E8%A9%9E-be-water/</a>"},{"pid":"1de2d46b684b1a16ef6a7a21e4f8c836b5947e3d","tid":1795791,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6954b4345bb40ed52633ef906c53d70021f0e55b","tid":1795791,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23aab08d19cbe3d094bac40b6ef424494f067658","tid":1795791,"uid":239105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9125db863cfd995b29d24df97c6c4c49ba461c6","tid":1795791,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ff18d9a823a327fe523431e3a721935_hd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic2.zhimg.com%2F50%2Fv2-5ff18d9a823a327fe523431e3a721935_hd.png&h=86526de1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb917d34477ed6e1fd95a6d7adee4c39a76ad7cd","tid":1795791,"uid":112878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:30:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"775a65e0bc68adefa0ebf8b82fc6644